 "version": "7.1.1"}, "id": "1160049024747028", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5437449896288644", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9158615487505381"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1160049024747028"}]}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1730884791, "id": "9158615487505381", "version": "7.1.1", "version_code": 219, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "9158611684172428"}, "asset_files": {"count": 89}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5437449896288644", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9158615487505381"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1160049024747028"}]}, "change_log": "We are excited to announce the **release of our new update** alongside with the start of a **new tournament season**.\nUsers in Early Access have shared positive feedback about this update, appreciating the enhanced realism of the gameplay.\n \n**Enhancements**\n\n**Realistic Bat Physics**\n- Updated bat powers to enhance the realism of bat physics\n- Ball movement when it takes an edge off the bat feels more natural\n\n**Bowling Enhancements**\n- Limited-over formats - Bowling strategies at higher difficulty levels now adapt based on user gameplay & More line and length variations from bowlers\n- In Unlimited over formats, bowling strategies including bowling spells and special deliveries, are updated according to user gameplay\n- Revised bowling regions for left-handed batsmen\n\n**Field Placement & Fielding Enhancements**\n- When the ball edges off the bat, the keeper and slips have an increased chance of taking a catch\n- Field placement adjusts based on your hitting regions as the match progresses and persists throughout the match\n- Updated ball deflection after misfields\n\n**Ball Physics**\n- Enhanced friction dynamics between the ball and grass\n- Increased ball bounce after pitching on all types of pitches\n- Reduced ball velocity upon pitching, with variations depending on the pitch type\n\n**Bug Fixes**\n- Reduced the gap between some of the commentary sentences\n- Resolved several disconnection issues in Co-Op to enhance multiplayer stability and performance\n\nThank you all for your continued support\n\n**To adapt to these enhancements, we recommend playing for 1-2 hours to adapt before jumping into competitive modes.**", "created_date": 1730702355, "id": "9144401815593415", "version": "7.1.0", "version_code": 218, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "9144399895593607"}, "asset_files": {"count": 89}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5437449896288644", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9158615487505381"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1725449773, "id": "8673052632728338", "version": "7.0.2", "version_code": 217, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8673050679395200"}, "asset_files": {"count": 89}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary"